title: SET_BIKE_ON_STAND
content:
0x9CFA4896C3A53CBB0x15D40761// SetBikeOnStand
void SET_BIKE_ON_STAND(Vehicle vehicle, float x, float y);Only works on bikes, both X and Y work in the -1 - 1 range.
X forces the bike to turn left or right (-1, 1)
Y forces the bike to lean to the left or to the right (-1, 1)
Example with X -1/Y 1
http://i.imgur.com/TgIuAPJ.jpg
Old name:  _SET_BIKE_LEAN_ANGLE
